node.text: "Don't get mad. Get even." ☝ In honor of #JohnTuckerMustDie's 15th anniversary, take a look back at these throwback interviews with the cast. #TheRewind

node.title: The Rewind: John Tucker Must Die

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 09, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Congrats are in order for Jennifer Love Hewitt—she has welcomed her third child with her husband, Brian. ❤️ Link in bio for the sweet announcement. (📷: Getty)

node.text: Clear eyes, full hearts, can't get over how Connie Britton is the cutest person on the planet. (📷: @conniebritton)

node.text: Hey #Dexter fans, we've got some chills for you. 👀 A new trailer for the show's revival finally reveals what became of his son and uh...let's just say history came a-knocking. Link in bio. (📷: YouTube/Showtime)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on September 09, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text: It's honestly so rude of Jonah Hill to get a girlfriend the minute we realized we were falling in love with him... All the deets on his new romance are in our bio. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 09, 2021 tagging @blakelively, and @vancityreynolds. May be an image of 2 people, outdoors and text that says '"I'M GRATEFUL FOR THE LIGHT AND FOR THE KINDNESS YOU SMUGGLE INTO EACH AND EVERY SECOND OF OUR LIVES." -RYAN REYNOLDS'.

node.text: ❗ This is not a breakup post. ❗ Actually, this is a tribute post to airport bathrooms. Happy anniversary, Blake & Ryan. (📷: Instagram)

node.text: Sofía Vergara's got talent—on screen, on stage, and in her closet. 🤩 Head to the link in our bio for her fall wardrobe must-haves that are so affordable, we almost didn't believe it. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 09, 2021 tagging @thelaurenkennedy, and @thejasonkennedy. May be an image of 1 person and lake.

node.text: Raise your hand if you watched the video of Jason Kennedy & his wife Lauren telling their friends they're expecting and fully bawled your eyes out. 🙋 Reactions from Justin & Hailey Bieber, Taylor Lautner, and more are in our bio. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on September 09, 2021 tagging @bravoandy. May be an image of 2 people, child and people sitting.

node.text: Clapback of the day goes to Andy Cohen, who had the best response when a troll slid into his DMs saying he should be a "better person for his son." The 🌶 receipts are in our bio. (📷: Instagram)
